    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/c74d663696aaad633d372a5e9dd50d9f.avif?t=1769650121\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >台湾早期1954年代，一位被宫庙收留的孤儿，无意间听到自己的身世，于是在大半夜瞒着宫庙，踏上寻亲的”奇幻之旅”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/0fdf053319a65eae4337c7f95a662b27.poster.avif?t=1769650121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/0fdf053319a65eae4337c7f95a662b27.webm?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/0fdf053319a65eae4337c7f95a662b27.mp4?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《打鬼》时空背景设定于台湾早期年代，真人故事改编，藉由游戏呈现人文精神、历史背景与台湾特有文化，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考据内容有台湾民初建筑、宫庙阵头、游戏角色外型与腔调。让玩家体验饱满的台湾特有风格与元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏为3D动作冒险游戏，在气氛绝佳的鬼城以3D第三人称玩法，武装自己，一路茁壮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从躲避鬼怪成长到能与之抗衡，挖掘鬼城被埋藏的过去、故事中震撼人心的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/85d45f9e01f55c67c33565f42cfc66b7.avif?t=1769650121\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单机故事模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/f7e82e04a8d09b31ff7ac87c1663937d.poster.avif?t=1769650121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/f7e82e04a8d09b31ff7ac87c1663937d.webm?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/f7e82e04a8d09b31ff7ac87c1663937d.mp4?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏为3D动作冒险游戏，在气氛绝佳的鬼城中以3D第三人称玩法，武装自己，一路茁壮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/4cfcfcc1271bbfb71f08753e6e376626.avif?t=1769650121\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•游戏中的剑术与刀术等，来自于武术教练与现役选手，采用动作捕捉技术，让玩家感受真实武术的威力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•法术与咒语，取材宗教为道教，由道长与宫庙指导制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•古早的机台、传统掷筊等结合台湾文化与宗教元素的解谜与小游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.poster.avif?t=1769650121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.webm?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.mp4?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•打鬼新乐风，东方乐器X金属乐X电子乐，让玩家拥有电影级般的享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•真实存在的鬼屋与宫庙阵头，制作团队亲身勘景与田野调查，也发生了不少&quot;灵异现象&quot;。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•故事模式支援多国语言（繁中、简中、英文、日文、韩文、俄文、法文、德文、西班牙文、葡萄牙文）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•支援Windows</p>",
